spec_data.Name: getdata-gzip
spec_data.Description:
Enables getdata to read dirfiles that are encoded (compressed) with gzip.
Fields must be fully compressed with gzip, not actively being written to.
Does not yet allow writing of gzip encoded dirfiles.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 03 Aug 2017 10:42:50 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Enables getdata read ability of gzip compressed dirfiles
